			"isDeleted": false,
			"boundElements": [],
			"updated": 1772820000000,
			"link": null,
			"locked": false,
			"text": "Dashed boxes = OVS bridges (Raikou)\nRounded boxes = Docker containers\nAll test traffic via Raikou OVS\nManagement: Docker 192.168.55.0/24\n\napp-router: CONNMARK policy routing\n  symmetric return paths per WAN\n  (replaces MASQUERADE on TCs)\n\nBoardfarm automation:\n  DUT ← LinuxSDWANRouter\n  TCs ← LinuxTrafficController\n  Client ← QoEClient\n\nEndpoints (from LAN):\n  http(s)://172.16.0.10 (prod)\n  http(s)://172.16.0.11 (stream)\n  wss://172.16.0.12:8443 (conf)\n  172.16.0.20 (IPsec hub)",
			"rawText": "Dashed boxes = OVS bridges (Raikou)\nRounded boxes = Docker containers\nAll test traffic via Raikou OVS\nManagement: Docker 192.168.55.0/24\n\napp-router: CONNMARK policy routing\n  symmetric return paths per WAN\n  (replaces MASQUERADE on TCs)\n\nBoardfarm automation:\n  DUT ← LinuxSDWANRouter\n  TCs ← LinuxTrafficController\n  Client ← QoEClient\n\nEndpoints (from LAN):\n  http(s)://172.16.0.10 (prod)\n  http(s)://172.16.0.11 (stream)\n  wss://172.16.0.12:8443 (conf)\n  172.16.0.20 (IPsec hub)",
			"fontSize": 16,
			"fontFamily": 5,
			"textAlign": "left",
			"verticalAlign": "top",
			"containerId": null,
			"originalText": "Dashed boxes = OVS bridges (Raikou)\nRounded boxes = Docker containers\nAll test traffic via Raikou OVS\nManagement: Docker 192.168.55.0/24\n\napp-router: CONNMARK policy routing\n  symmetric return paths per WAN\n  (replaces MASQUERADE on TCs)\n\nBoardfarm automation:\n  DUT ← LinuxSDWANRouter\n  TCs ← LinuxTrafficController\n  Client ← QoEClient\n\nEndpoints (from LAN):\n  http(s)://172.16.0.10 (prod)\n  http(s)://172.16.0.11 (stream)\n  wss://172.16.0.12:8443 (conf)\n  172.16.0.20 (IPsec hub)",
			"autoResize": true,
			"lineHeight": 1.25,
			"hasTextLink": false
		},
